{"tid":344684,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《聖鬥士星矢》將推出重製版動畫好萊塢團隊寫劇本","createTime":"2017-08-02T12:26:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-04T04:41:16.000Z","uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8d1fab37909d094599c1013deb2334d3da7295d9","tid":344684,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T12:26:24.000Z","msg":"提到日本動漫作品《聖鬥士星矢》，可以說是很多人的童年，一直到今天都是大家心中經典。現在這部作宣布將要推出重製版動畫，仍將由東映製作，動畫將在Netflix播出。官方還公開了動畫的視覺圖，動畫第一季預計全12話，劇情將從&ldquo;銀河戰爭篇&rdquo;到&ldquo;白銀聖鬥士篇&rdquo;，每集30分鐘。這個消息也是粉絲們非常激動，官方目前還沒有公開更多的消息，動漫星空也將會持續關注。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/az6hI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2Faz6hI.jpg&h=afebfb7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在這張視覺圖上，我們看到重製版動畫標題為《Knights of the Zodiac：聖鬥士星矢》，還有在聖域中星矢向雅典娜女神效忠的場景，真是非常勾起大家的回憶啊。好期待能夠快點看到重製版的動畫。《聖鬥士星矢》重製版監督將由蘆野芳晴擔任，腳本由好萊塢腳本家團隊執筆，動畫採用CG製作。"},{"pid":"71eb6795e088fd9ed52f6871bd98e773f54d7820","tid":344684,"uid":36287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T12:27:24.000Z","msg":"出lc好過啦"},{"pid":"ffb21d9e4839d1cada95e699bdeeedc9a21f1707","tid":344684,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T12:27:38.000Z","msg":"未睇過星矢,如果重制左都想睇下<br />\n希望畫風唔好太美式"},{"pid":"e8619eefea4a6443b655ea7f8afad6e949c83da8","tid":344684,"uid":19925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T12:47:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出lc好過啦</blockquote><br />\n原作唔like+賣唔出"},{"pid":"82f8e61320adc0e98eb9e2b788a4fd22d95c849a","tid":344684,"uid":82743,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:01:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出lc好過啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當年果個聲優陣容....<br />\n好想睇佢整埋落去....超like lc全部黃金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b042ea23b2e3a92568741a357e5d081cb9bcd7","tid":344684,"uid":15620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T03:20:34.000Z","msg":"之前係咪打到冥王就完左?"},{"pid":"17e79d1a5bcf8e4d006e9adeac1d10b14ee3236b","tid":344684,"uid":117552,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T04:02:27.000Z","msg":"LC同冥王十二宮篇最高質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eaaafd2adc433826e91704ac3d462894b554d1d","tid":344684,"uid":55598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T04:33:02.000Z","msg":"唔好啦，白銀根本唔好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"700c25931d46a9aa3bcf0c30416c5815aa9cb42c","tid":344684,"uid":48222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-04T04:41:16.000Z","msg":"冇興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係想睇LC"}]}